monitor and manage your application using various endpoints 

     <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
      <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-actuator</artifactId>
    </dependency>


management.endpoints.web.exposure.include=*  //exposes all endpoints 
management.endpoints.web.exposure.include=health,info,metrics,loggers   // for specific use comma seperated 

Health Checks /health

Metrics  /metrics    /metrics/metricName 

Env /env configs , system settings 

beans /beans 

/mappings 

/loggers -> view and change logging level at runtime 

